{"tid":1997167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣以外國種族滅絕日為國慶合適嗎？","createTime":"2020-05-01T12:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T13:32:58.000Z","uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"405aef247d15c943b53f662d6742c05aa61bee01","tid":1997167,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:49:12.000Z","msg":"辛亥是一場針對&ldquo;韃虜&rdquo;的種族滅絕，時為日本領土的台灣并非共犯，而且沒有辛亥就沒有外來政權和二二八。在道德責任和歷史關聯兩方面，台灣人都不宜與外國政黨一起慶祝其先輩的罪行。相對於台中兩國&rdquo;同文同種&ldquo;的勉强，奧地利原系德意志邦聯成員，但奧地利不像台灣慶祝雙十那樣紀念德國成功興建奧斯維辛。<br />\n<br />\n延申閲讀：國民黨掩埋的辛亥革命真相：一段不下於納粹的種族屠殺史，孩子的娛樂就是比賽數屍體 （<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/2017/02/15/the-truth-of-double-ten/）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2F2017%2F02%2F15%2Fthe-truth-of-double-ten%2F%EF%BC%89&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1%2FZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=db0c8b8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/2017/02/15/the-truth-of-double-ten/）</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EW5mWOzUYAA4GDd?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEW5mWOzUYAA4GDd%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=996f90a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfb03ef86af25f6deeb706bc1d6f2359824196c8","tid":1997167,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:50:47.000Z","msg":"一起底全部殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96dd18995e348afe3a2e7ca4015b4eb8ee453a0","tid":1997167,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfb03ef86af25f6deeb706bc1d6f2359824196c8","tid":1997167,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:50:47.000Z","msg":"一起底全部殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"我不是华人，简体字和繁体字都不是我的文字。<br />\n你们有你们的正体字，我们有我们的正体字（图）。<br />\n我们的传统是用阿拉伯字母拼写汉语。不妨相互尊重。<br />\n你们华人里面有不少种族主义者，希望你不是其中之一。<br />\n<